OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781606875
OL,3,CHundreds of fish dead after suspected
OL,4,Cpollution incident
OL,6,FImages shared by NRW show dead fish at
OL,7,Fthe bottom of the small stream, which
OL,8,Fwas recently identified as one of the
OL,9,Fmost polluted urban watercourses
OL,10,Fexamined in Wales.
OL,12,FIt comes after images showing the
OL,13,Fstream, which runs through Roath Park,
OL,14,Fappeared to have turned white were
OL,15,Fshared on social media.
OL,17,FIt's suspected the fish deaths may
OL,18,Fhave been caused by something toxic
OL,19,Fbeing poured down a surface water
OL,20,Fdrain, or a larger scale pollution,
OL,21,FNRW said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
