OL,3,CHundreds of fish dead after suspected
OL,4,Cpollution incident
OL,6,FOfficers are investigating the cause
OL,7,Fand have appealed to anyone with
OL,8,Finformation about what might have
OL,9,Fhappened at Roath Brook to get in
OL,10,Ftouch.
OL,12,FIt is believed the pollutant has
OL,13,Fpassed through the brook now but dog
OL,14,Fowners may want to keep their pets out
OL,15,Fof the water as a precautionary
OL,16,Fmeasure, the organisation said in an
OL,17,Fupdate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
