OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781606875
OL,3,CHundreds of fish dead after suspected
OL,4,Cpollution incident
OL,6,FNRW added that live fish have been
OL,7,Fobserved in the nearby brook at
OL,8,FWaterloo Gardens since the pollution
OL,9,Fincident was reported.
OL,11,FIt reminded members of the public that
OL,12,Fonly rainwater should go down surface
OL,13,Fwater drains. "Harmful chemicals,
OL,14,Foils, paints, or cleaning products can
OL,15,Fcause serious damage to local wildlife
OL,16,Fand ecosystems if disposed of
OL,17,Fincorrectly," NRW said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
